</section>

<section style="padding-bottom:40px">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head"><div class="kicker">The New, Streamlined Flow</div><h2>Apply → Pay → Screen, automatically</h2><p>Everything happens in one secure portal. Your screening reports are delivered to us instantly — no manual data entry on our end.</p></div>
    <div class="grid4">
      <div class="card center"><div class="ic" style="margin:0 auto 1rem">📝</div><h3>1. Apply</h3><p>Complete the online application below in about 10 minutes.</p></div>
      <div class="card center"><div class="ic" style="margin:0 auto 1rem">💳</div><h3>2. Pay fee</h3><p>Pay your application fee securely online (card or bank).</p></div>
      <div class="card center"><div class="ic" style="margin:0 auto 1rem">🔒</div><h3>3. Screen securely</h3><p>You enter your SSN directly with the screening bureau — we never see or store it.</p></div>
      <div class="card center"><div class="ic" style="margin:0 auto 1rem">✅</div><h3>4. Get a decision</h3><p>Credit, criminal &amp; eviction reports are returned to us automatically.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding-top:20px">
  <div class="wrap" style="max-width:860px">
    <div class="form-card">
      <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.6rem;margin-bottom:1.4rem">
        <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem">Rental Application</h2>
        <span class="secure-tag">🔒 Secure &amp; encrypted</span>
      </div>
      <form onsubmit="this.style.display='none';document.getElementById('done').style.display='block';window.scrollTo(0,0);return false">
        <div class="fsec"><h4><span class="num">1</span> Applicant Information</h4>
          <div class="frow"><div class="field"><label>First name</label><input required></div><div class="field"><label>Last name</label><input required></div></div>
          <div class="frow three"><div class="field"><label>Date of birth</label><input type="date" required></div><div class="field"><label>Email</label><input type="email" required></div><div class="field"><label>Phone</label><input type="tel" required></div></div>
          <div class="frow"><div class="field"><label>Driver's license / ID #</label><input></div><div class="field"><label>Issuing state</label><input placeholder="FL"></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="fsec"><h4><span class="num">2</span> Property You're Applying For</h4>
          <div class="frow one"><div class="field"><label>Rental address or listing</label><input required placeholder="123 Bayshore Blvd, Tampa, FL"></div></div>
          <div class="frow"><div class="field"><label>Desired move-in date</label><input type="date"></div><div class="field"><label>Desired lease term</label><select><option>12 months</option><option>Other (ask us)</option></select></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="fsec"><h4><span class="num">3</span> Residence History</h4>
          <div class="frow one"><div class="field"><label>Current street address</label><input required></div></div>
          <div class="frow three"><div class="field"><label>City</label><input required></div><div class="field"><label>State</label><input required></div><div class="field"><label>ZIP</label><input required></div></div>
          <div class="frow three"><div class="field"><label>Years at address</label><input placeholder="2"></div><div class="field"><label>Monthly rent/mortgage</label><input placeholder="$1,800"></div><div class="field"><label>Reason for moving</label><input></div></div>
          <div class="frow"><div class="field"><label>Current landlord name</label><input></div><div class="field"><label>Landlord phone</label><input type="tel"></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="fsec"><h4><span class="num">4</span> Employment &amp; Income</h4>
          <div class="frow"><div class="field"><label>Employer</label><input required></div><div class="field"><label>Job title</label><input></div></div>
          <div class="frow three"><div class="field"><label>Gross monthly income</label><input required placeholder="$5,500"></div><div class="field"><label>Years employed</label><input placeholder="3"></div><div class="field"><label>Supervisor phone</label><input type="tel"></div></div>
          <div class="frow one"><div class="field"><label>Additional income (optional)</label><input placeholder="Source &amp; amount"></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="fsec"><h4><span class="num">5</span> Occupants, Pets &amp; Vehicles</h4>
          <div class="frow three"><div class="field"><label># of occupants</label><input placeholder="2"></div><div class="field"><label># of pets</label><input placeholder="1"></div><div class="field"><label># of vehicles</label><input placeholder="2"></div></div>
          <div class="frow one"><div class="field"><label>Pet details (type, breed, weight)</label><input placeholder="e.g., 1 dog, Labrador, 60 lbs"></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="fsec"><h4><span class="num">6</span> Emergency Contact &amp; Reference</h4>
          <div class="frow three"><div class="field"><label>Contact name</label><input></div><div class="field"><label>Relationship</label><input></div><div class="field"><label>Phone</label><input type="tel"></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="fsec"><h4><span class="num">7</span> Consent &amp; Screening</h4>
          <div class="note-box mb1">
            <b>About your Social Security number:</b> You will <u>not</u> enter your SSN on this form. After you submit and pay the application fee, you'll be redirected to our screening partner's secure portal where you enter your SSN <b>directly with the bureau</b>. We receive your credit, criminal, and eviction results — but never see or store your SSN. This keeps your information safe and is fully FCRA-compliant.
          </div>
          <label style="display:flex;gap:.6rem;align-items:flex-start;font-size:.92rem;color:var(--muted)"><input type="checkbox" required style="margin-top:.3rem;width:auto"> I authorize Tampa Bay Property Experts and its screening partner to obtain consumer/credit, criminal background, and eviction reports, and I certify the information provided is accurate.</label>
        </div>
        <div class="fsec"><h4><span class="num">8</span> Application Fee</h4>
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;background:var(--soft);border-radius:12px;padding:16px 20px;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.6rem">
            <div><b style="font-family:'Space Grotesk';font-size:1.15rem;color:var(--navy)">Application fee</b><div style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--muted)">Per adult applicant · covers screening reports</div></div>
            <div style="font-family:'Space Grotesk';font-size:1.6rem;color:var(--teal-d);font-weight:700">$49.90</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" type="submit" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;margin-top:1.4rem">Submit Application &amp; Continue to Payment →</button>
        <p class="center" style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--muted-2);margin-top:.7rem">Demo form. At launch this connects to your property management software, which handles payment and screening automatically.</p>
      </form>
      <div id="done" style="display:none;text-align:center;padding:30px">
        <div style="font-size:2.6rem">✅</div>
        <h2>Application received!</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:46ch;margin:.6rem auto 0">In the live version you'd now be taken to pay your fee and complete secure SSN screening with our bureau partner. We'll be in touch within 1–2 business days.</p>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/" style="margin-top:1.2rem">Back to home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
